\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}
name: ralph\PYGZhy{}init
description: Bootstrap the Ralph e2e test generation loop into the current repo. Scaffolds scripts and prompt templates for an autonomous Playwright test writing loop driven by user stories and plan.json files.
\PYG{g+gu}{allowed\PYGZus{}tools: Read, Write, Edit, Bash, Glob}
\PYG{g+gu}{\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}}

\PYG{g+gh}{\PYGZsh{} Ralph Init}

Scaffold the Ralph autonomous e2e test generation loop into the current repository. This creates the scripts and prompt templates needed to run Codex in an iterative loop that autonomously writes Playwright e2e tests from pre\PYGZhy{}generated user stories and plan.json files.

Reference: https://www.aihero.dev/tips\PYGZhy{}for\PYGZhy{}ai\PYGZhy{}coding\PYGZhy{}with\PYGZhy{}ralph\PYGZhy{}wiggum

\PYG{g+gu}{\PYGZsh{}\PYGZsh{} Pipeline}

This skill is designed to work as the final step in this pipeline:

\PYG{k}{1.} \PYG{g+gs}{**generate\PYGZhy{}user\PYGZhy{}stories**} → reads \PYG{l+s+sb}{`RouteConfig.tsx`}, generates user story markdown files in \PYG{l+s+sb}{`apps/client/playwright/user\PYGZhy{}stories/`}
\PYG{k}{2.} \PYG{g+gs}{**user\PYGZhy{}story\PYGZhy{}to\PYGZhy{}plan\PYGZhy{}json**} → reads a user story, generates \PYG{l+s+sb}{`apps/client/playwright/plans/\PYGZlt{}story\PYGZgt{}.json`}
\PYG{k}{3.} \PYG{g+gs}{**ralph\PYGZhy{}init**} (this skill) → scaffolds the loop scripts to execute the plans

\PYG{g+gs}{**Prerequisites:**} Steps 1 and 2 must be completed before running Ralph. Ralph does NOT generate user stories or plan.json files — the user is expected to have generated those beforehand.

\PYG{g+gu}{\PYGZsh{}\PYGZsh{}\PYGZsh{} Key artifacts}

| Artifact | Location | Generated by |
|\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}|\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}|\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}|
| User stories | \PYG{l+s+sb}{`apps/client/playwright/user\PYGZhy{}stories/\PYGZlt{}role\PYGZgt{}/\PYGZlt{}story\PYGZgt{}.md`} | \PYG{l+s+sb}{`generate\PYGZhy{}user\PYGZhy{}stories`} skill |
| Plan files | \PYG{l+s+sb}{`apps/client/playwright/plans/\PYGZlt{}story\PYGZgt{}.json`} | \PYG{l+s+sb}{`user\PYGZhy{}story\PYGZhy{}to\PYGZhy{}plan\PYGZhy{}json`} skill |
| Progress logs | \PYG{l+s+sb}{`apps/client/playwright/plans/\PYGZlt{}story\PYGZgt{}.progress.md`} | Ralph (at runtime) |
| Spec files | \PYG{l+s+sb}{`apps/client/playwright/e2e/\PYGZlt{}story\PYGZgt{}.spec.ts`} | Ralph (at runtime) |
| POM pages | \PYG{l+s+sb}{`apps/client/playwright/support/pages/\PYGZlt{}feature\PYGZgt{}Page.ts`} | Ralph (at runtime) |
| Fixtures | \PYG{l+s+sb}{`apps/client/playwright/fixtures/\PYGZlt{}feature\PYGZgt{}.fixtures.ts`} | Ralph (at runtime) |

\PYG{g+gu}{\PYGZsh{}\PYGZsh{} Steps}

\PYG{k}{1.} Check what already exists — don\PYGZsq{}t overwrite any existing Ralph files without asking
\PYG{k}{2.} Verify prerequisites:
\PYG{+w}{   }\PYG{k}{\PYGZhy{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s+sb}{`apps/client/playwright/user\PYGZhy{}stories/`} must have user story files
\PYG{+w}{   }\PYG{k}{\PYGZhy{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s+sb}{`apps/client/playwright/plans/`} must have at least one plan.json file
\PYG{+w}{   }\PYG{k}{\PYGZhy{}}\PYG{+w}{ }If either is missing, tell the user to run the prerequisite skills first
\PYG{k}{3.} Scan \PYG{l+s+sb}{`apps/client/playwright/plans/`} to count total plans and plans with incomplete tasks
\PYG{k}{4.} Create the following files (skip any that already exist and are valid):

\PYG{g+gu}{\PYGZsh{}\PYGZsh{}\PYGZsh{} `scripts/ralph.sh`}

An executable bash script that:

\PYG{k}{\PYGZhy{}}\PYG{+w}{ }Takes an iteration count as the first argument (default: 5)
\PYG{k}{\PYGZhy{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{g+gs}{**Accepts `\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}story=\PYGZlt{}name\PYGZgt{}` to work on a specific plan**} (optional):
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{k}{\PYGZhy{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s+sb}{`\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}story=jobs\PYGZhy{}detail`} → plan at \PYG{l+s+sb}{`apps/client/playwright/plans/jobs\PYGZhy{}detail.json`}, user story resolved from the plan\PYGZsq{}s \PYG{l+s+sb}{`source.user\PYGZus{}story`} field, progress at \PYG{l+s+sb}{`apps/client/playwright/plans/jobs\PYGZhy{}detail.progress.md`}
\PYG{k}{\PYGZhy{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{g+gs}{**Without `\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}story`**}: scans \PYG{l+s+sb}{`apps/client/playwright/plans/`} for all \PYG{l+s+sb}{`.json`} files with incomplete tasks (\PYG{l+s+sb}{`\PYGZdq{}passes\PYGZdq{}: false`}), processes them sequentially in alphabetical order
\PYG{k}{\PYGZhy{}}\PYG{+w}{ }Loops N times, each time calling \PYG{l+s+sb}{`codex exec`} with the iteration prompt, passing the plan file, user story, and progress log as context
\PYG{k}{\PYGZhy{}}\PYG{+w}{ }After each iteration, checks stdout for \PYG{l+s+sb}{`\PYGZlt{}promise\PYGZgt{}COMPLETE\PYGZlt{}/promise\PYGZgt{}`} — if found (all tasks in current plan complete), moves to the next incomplete plan or exits if all plans are done
\PYG{k}{\PYGZhy{}}\PYG{+w}{ }Includes a \PYG{l+s+sb}{`\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}hitl`} flag that runs one iteration, then writes the prompt context to a temp file and starts \PYG{l+s+sb}{`codex`} in interactive TUI mode so the user can review and give feedback within the same session
\PYG{k}{\PYGZhy{}}\PYG{+w}{ }Supports \PYG{l+s+sb}{`\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}afk`} flag for fully autonomous mode — implies \PYG{l+s+sb}{`\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}yolo`}, uses the AFK\PYGZhy{}specific prompt (\PYG{l+s+sb}{`prompts/ralph\PYGZhy{}iteration\PYGZhy{}afk.md`}) that instructs Ralph to make all decisions independently
\PYG{k}{\PYGZhy{}}\PYG{+w}{ }Supports \PYG{l+s+sb}{`\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}sandbox`} flag to use Codex\PYGZsq{}s built\PYGZhy{}in sandbox (\PYG{l+s+sb}{`\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}sandbox danger\PYGZhy{}full\PYGZhy{}access`}) for controlled execution
\PYG{k}{\PYGZhy{}}\PYG{+w}{ }Supports \PYG{l+s+sb}{`\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}yolo`} flag to run with \PYG{l+s+sb}{`\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}yolo`} (\PYG{l+s+sb}{`\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}dangerously\PYGZhy{}bypass\PYGZhy{}approvals\PYGZhy{}and\PYGZhy{}sandbox`}) for fully autonomous operation (no approval prompts, no sandbox)

Example structure:

\PYG{l+s+sb}{```bash}
\PYG{c+ch}{\PYGZsh{}!/usr/bin/env bash}
\PYG{n+nb}{set}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYGZhy{}e

\PYG{n+nv}{PLANS\PYGZus{}DIR}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}apps/client/playwright/plans\PYGZdq{}}
\PYG{n+nv}{ITERATIONS}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{l+m}{5}
\PYG{n+nv}{STORY}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}\PYGZdq{}}
\PYG{n+nv}{HITL}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{n+nb}{false}
\PYG{n+nv}{AFK}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{n+nb}{false}
\PYG{n+nv}{SANDBOX}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{n+nb}{false}
\PYG{n+nv}{YOLO}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{n+nb}{false}

\PYG{k}{while}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{[[}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n+nv}{\PYGZdl{}\PYGZsh{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYGZhy{}gt\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+m}{0}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{]]}\PYG{p}{;}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k}{do}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{k}{case}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{n+nv}{\PYGZdl{}1}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k}{in}
\PYG{+w}{    }\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}hitl\PYG{o}{)}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n+nv}{HITL}\PYG{o}{=}true\PYG{p}{;}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n+nv}{ITERATIONS}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{l+m}{1}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{p}{;;}
\PYG{+w}{    }\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}afk\PYG{o}{)}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n+nv}{AFK}\PYG{o}{=}true\PYG{p}{;}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n+nv}{YOLO}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{n+nb}{true}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{p}{;;}
\PYG{+w}{    }\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}sandbox\PYG{o}{)}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n+nv}{SANDBOX}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{n+nb}{true}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{p}{;;}
\PYG{+w}{    }\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}yolo\PYG{o}{)}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n+nv}{YOLO}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{n+nb}{true}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{p}{;;}
\PYG{+w}{    }\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}story\PYG{o}{=}*\PYG{o}{)}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n+nv}{STORY}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{l+s+si}{\PYGZdl{}\PYGZob{}}\PYG{n+nv}{1}\PYG{p}{\PYGZsh{}*=}\PYG{l+s+si}{\PYGZcb{}}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{p}{;;}
\PYG{+w}{    }\PYG{o}{[}\PYG{l+m}{0}\PYGZhy{}9\PYG{o}{]}*\PYG{o}{)}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n+nv}{ITERATIONS}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{n+nv}{\PYGZdl{}1}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{p}{;;}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{k}{esac}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{n+nb}{shift}
\PYG{k}{done}

\PYG{n+nv}{CODEX\PYGZus{}FLAGS}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}sandbox workspace\PYGZhy{}write\PYGZdq{}}
\PYG{k}{if}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{[}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{n+nv}{\PYGZdl{}YOLO}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n+nb}{true}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{]}\PYG{p}{;}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k}{then}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{n+nv}{CODEX\PYGZus{}FLAGS}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}\PYGZhy{}\PYGZhy{}yolo\PYGZdq{}}
\PYG{k}{fi}

\PYG{n+nv}{PROMPT\PYGZus{}FILE}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}prompts/ralph\PYGZhy{}iteration.md\PYGZdq{}}
\PYG{k}{if}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{[}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{n+nv}{\PYGZdl{}HITL}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n+nb}{true}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{]}\PYG{p}{;}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k}{then}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{n+nv}{PROMPT\PYGZus{}FILE}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}prompts/ralph\PYGZhy{}iteration\PYGZhy{}hitl.md\PYGZdq{}}
\PYG{k}{elif}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{[}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{n+nv}{\PYGZdl{}AFK}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{n+nb}{true}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{]}\PYG{p}{;}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k}{then}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{n+nv}{PROMPT\PYGZus{}FILE}\PYG{o}{=}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}prompts/ralph\PYGZhy{}iteration\PYGZhy{}afk.md\PYGZdq{}}
\PYG{k}{fi}

\PYG{c+c1}{\PYGZsh{} Build list of plan files to process}
\PYG{k}{if}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{[}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYGZhy{}n\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{n+nv}{\PYGZdl{}STORY}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{]}\PYG{p}{;}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k}{then}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{n+nv}{PLAN\PYGZus{}FILES}\PYG{o}{=(}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{l+s+si}{\PYGZdl{}\PYGZob{}}\PYG{n+nv}{PLANS\PYGZus{}DIR}\PYG{l+s+si}{\PYGZcb{}}\PYG{l+s+s2}{/}\PYG{l+s+si}{\PYGZdl{}\PYGZob{}}\PYG{n+nv}{STORY}\PYG{l+s+si}{\PYGZcb{}}\PYG{l+s+s2}{.json\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{o}{)}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{k}{if}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{[}\PYG{+w}{ }!\PYG{+w}{ }\PYGZhy{}f\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{l+s+si}{\PYGZdl{}\PYGZob{}}\PYG{n+nv}{PLAN\PYGZus{}FILES}\PYG{p}{[0]}\PYG{l+s+si}{\PYGZcb{}}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{o}{]}\PYG{p}{;}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k}{then}
\PYG{+w}{    }\PYG{n+nb}{echo}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}Error: plan not found: }\PYG{l+s+si}{\PYGZdl{}\PYGZob{}}\PYG{n+nv}{PLAN\PYGZus{}FILES}\PYG{p}{[0]}\PYG{l+s+si}{\PYGZcb{}}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYGZgt{}\PYG{p}{\PYGZam{}}\PYG{l+m}{2}
\PYG{+w}{    }\PYG{n+nb}{exit}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+m}{1}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{k}{fi}
\PYG{k}{else}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{c+c1}{\PYGZsh{} Find all plans with incomplete tasks (has \PYGZdq{}passes\PYGZdq{}: false), sorted alphabetically}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{n+nv}{PLAN\PYGZus{}FILES}\PYG{o}{=()}
\PYG{+w}{  }\PYG{k}{for}\PYG{+w}{ }f\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k}{in}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k}{\PYGZdl{}(}ls\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{l+s+si}{\PYGZdl{}\PYGZob{}}\PYG{n+nv}{PLANS\PYGZus{}DIR}\PYG{l+s+si}{\PYGZcb{}}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}/*.json\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+m}{2}\PYGZgt{}/dev/null\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{p}{|}\PYG{+w}{ }sort\PYG{k}{)}\PYG{p}{;}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k}{do}
\PYG{+w}{    }\PYG{k}{if}\PYG{+w}{ }grep\PYG{+w}{ }\PYGZhy{}q\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s+s1}{\PYGZsq{}\PYGZdq{}passes\PYGZdq{}: false\PYGZsq{}}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{n+nv}{\PYGZdl{}f}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{p}{;}\PYG{+w}{ }\PYG{k}{then}
\PYG{+w}{      }\PYG{n+nv}{PLAN\PYGZus{}FILES}\PYG{o}{+=(}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{n+nv}{\PYGZdl{}f}\PYG{l+s+s2}{\PYGZdq{}}\PYG{o}{)}
\PYG{+w}{    }\PYG{k}{fi}
